Body:
Description: After adding a valid license via the gui and restarting the system, on startup the message is displayed "[FAILED] Failed to start A high performance web server and reverse proxy server".
The server continues the startup however the website is not reachable

What We've Learned Updated: - Client reporting  that he is unable to start nginx webserver 
- Sent client email requesting availability for joining a remote session or when would he would be available to join a remote session
